name: Dominique D'Angelo (MiniJello)
description:
Dominique D'Angelo, better known as MiniJello. Five or six years ago, a very popular Instagram model among "boobs on a stick" lovers, she became a legend in this community.

It was very difficult to create this TI, there is no good quality photo of her, especially where her face could be clearly seen. Therefore, it took me several attempts to create at least such a result. I think in the future I will update this version.

I hope someone likes this TI. As always, I will be happy to receive a review or feedback.
